ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanadian Public Health Association ** Ex-Gratia payments **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Canadian Heritage to make a one-time ex gratia payments of $100,000 to the CANADIAN PUBLIC HEALTH ASSOCIATION, in support of Immunize Canada, in honour of the birth of Her Royal Highness Princess Charlotte of Cambridge.
